    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The first distinctive Australian coins, created by overstriking Pieces of Eight from which the center had been punched out; issued between 1813 and 1829 and valued at 5 shillings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000012271/Doty, Macmillan Encyclopedic Dictionary of Numismatics (1982)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Las primeras monedas características de Australia, creadas por sobreimprimir duros de los cuales el centro ha sido perforado; emitidas entre 1813 y 1829 y con un valor de 5 chelines.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>De eerste echte Australische munten die werden gemaakt door het overslaan van stukken van achten waaruit het midden was verwijderd. Ze werden tussen 1813 en 1829 uitgegeven en hadden een waarde van vijf shilling.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>最早的澳洲特有硬幣，將新的圖樣幣值壓印至八里爾銀幣上，錢幣中央已打了一個孔。於西元1813年至1829年間發行，幣值為五先令。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
